<text><body>
<pb n="0421a" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0453.0421a"/>
<lb n="0421a01" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0421a02" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 453 [Nos. 454, 455]</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0421a03" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0421001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛說＝觀【宋】【元】【宮】，佛說觀【明】</note><note n="0421001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛說【大】，觀【宋】【元】【宮】，佛說觀【明】</note><app n="0421001"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">觀</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">佛說觀</rdg></app>彌<note n="0421002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勒＋（菩薩）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">勒【大】，勒菩薩【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421002"><lem wit="【大】">勒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">勒菩薩</rdg></app>下生經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0421a04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0421a05" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator"><note n="0421003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">西晉…譯＝諸藏經并品次並闕譯人【宮】</note><note n="0421003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">西晉…譯【大】，諸藏經并品次並闕譯人【宮】</note><app n="0421003" cb:word-count="10"><lem wit="【大】">西晉月氏三藏竺法<note n="0421004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">護＋（單）【元】【明】</note><note n="0421004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">護【大】，護單【元】【明】</note><app n="0421004"><lem wit="【大】">護</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">護單</rdg></app>譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">諸藏經并品次並闕譯人</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0421a06" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT14p0421a0601">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421a0604" rend="inline">一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園，
<lb n="0421a07" ed="T"/>與大比丘眾<note n="0421005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（千）＋五【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">五【大】，千五【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421005"><lem wit="【大】">五</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">千五</rdg></app>百人俱。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421a0710" rend="inline">爾時，阿難偏<note n="0421006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">露＝袒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">露【大】，袒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421006"><lem wit="【大】">露</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">袒</rdg></app>
<lb n="0421a08" ed="T"/>右<note n="0421007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">肩＝臂【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">肩【大】，臂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421007"><lem wit="【大】">肩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">臂</rdg></app>，右膝著地，白<note n="0421008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＝世尊【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，世尊【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421008"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">世尊</rdg></app>言：「如來玄鑒，無事
<lb n="0421a09" ed="T"/>不察，當來、過去、現在三世，皆悉明了；過去諸
<lb n="0421a10" ed="T"/>佛姓字、名號，弟子、菩薩、翼從多少，皆悉知之；
<lb n="0421a11" ed="T"/>一劫、百劫、若無數劫，皆悉觀察，亦復<note n="0421009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如是＝知【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如是【大】，知【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421009"><lem wit="【大】">如是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">知</rdg></app>；
<lb n="0421a12" ed="T"/>國王、大臣、人民姓字<note n="0421010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則＝悉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則【大】，悉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421010"><lem wit="【大】">則</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">悉</rdg></app>能分別；如今現在國
<lb n="0421a13" ed="T"/>界若干亦復明了。將來久遠彌勒出現，至真、
<lb n="0421a14" ed="T"/>等正覺，欲聞其變，弟子、翼從，佛境豐樂，為
<lb n="0421a15" ed="T"/>經幾時？」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421a1504" rend="inline">佛告阿難：「汝還就坐，聽我所說
<lb n="0421a16" ed="T"/>彌勒出現國土豐樂、弟子多少。善思念之，執
<lb n="0421a17" ed="T"/>在心懷。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421a1704" rend="inline">是時，阿難從佛受教，即還就坐。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421a1716" rend="inline">爾
<lb n="0421a18" ed="T"/>時，世尊告阿難曰：「將來久遠於此國界
<lb n="0421a19" ed="T"/>當有城郭名曰<note n="0421011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">翅＝雞【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">翅【大】，雞【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421011"><lem wit="【大】">翅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雞</rdg></app>頭，東西十二由旬，南北
<lb n="0421a20" ed="T"/>七由旬，土地豐熟，人民熾盛，街巷成行。爾時，
<lb n="0421a21" ed="T"/>城中有龍王名曰水光，夜雨香澤，晝則清
<lb n="0421a22" ed="T"/>和。是時，<note n="0421012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">翅頭＝雞頭【宮】下同</note><note n="0421012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">翅頭【大】下同，雞頭【宮】下同</note><app n="0421012"><lem wit="【大】">翅頭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">雞頭</rdg></app>城中有羅剎鬼名曰葉華，所
<lb n="0421a23" ed="T"/>行順法不違正教，<note n="0421013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">每向＝每何【三】，教伺【宮】</note><note n="0421013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">每向【大】，每何【宋】【元】【明】，教伺【宮】</note><app n="0421013"><lem wit="【大】">每向</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">每何</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">教伺</rdg></app>人民寢寐之後，
<lb n="0421a24" ed="T"/>除去穢惡諸不淨者；<note n="0421014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＝又【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常【大】，又【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421014"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">又</rdg></app>以香汁而灑其地，
<lb n="0421a25" ed="T"/>極為香淨。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421a2505" rend="inline">「阿難<note n="0421015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當知爾時＝當爾之時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當知爾時【大】，當爾之時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421015"><lem wit="【大】">當知，爾時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">當爾之時</rdg></app>閻<note n="0421016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">浮＋（提）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">浮【大】，浮提【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421016"><lem wit="【大】">浮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">浮提</rdg></app>地東西
<lb n="0421a26" ed="T"/>南北<note n="0421017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">千＝十【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">千【大】，十【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421017"><lem wit="【大】">千</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">十</rdg></app>萬由旬，諸山河石壁皆自消滅，四大
<lb n="0421a27" ed="T"/>海水各<note n="0421018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">減＝據【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">減【大】，據【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421018"><lem wit="【大】">減</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">據</rdg></app>一<note n="0421019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">萬＝方【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">萬【大】，方【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421019"><lem wit="【大】">萬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">方</rdg></app>。時閻浮地極為平整，如
<lb n="0421a28" ed="T"/>鏡清明。舉閻浮地內穀食豐賤，人民熾盛，
<lb n="0421a29" ed="T"/>多諸珍寶。<note n="0421020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸村落相近＝諸村聚落【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸村落相近【大】，諸村聚落【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421020"><lem wit="【大】">諸村落相近</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">諸村聚落</rdg></app>，鷄鳴相接。是時，弊
<pb n="0421b" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0453.0421b"/>
<lb n="0421b01" ed="T"/>華果樹枯竭，穢惡亦自消滅；其餘甘美果樹、
<lb n="0421b02" ed="T"/>香氣殊好者皆生于地。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421b0210" rend="inline">「爾時，時氣和適四時
<lb n="0421b03" ed="T"/>順節，人身之中無有百八之患：貪欲、瞋恚、
<lb n="0421b04" ed="T"/>愚癡、不大慇懃。人心均平，皆同一意，相見歡
<lb n="0421b05" ed="T"/>悅，善言相向。言辭一類無有差別，如彼<note n="0421021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">優單越＝欝單越【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0421021" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->優單越【大】＊，欝單越【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0421021"><lem wit="【大】">優
<lb n="0421b06" ed="T"/>單越</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">欝單越</rdg></app>人而無有異。是時，閻浮地內人民大
<lb n="0421b07" ed="T"/>小皆同<note n="0421022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一向無＝一響無有【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一向無【大】，一響無有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421022"><lem wit="【大】">一向，無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">一響無有</rdg></app>若干<note n="0421023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421023"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>差<note n="0421024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">別＋（異）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">別【大】，別異【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421024"><lem wit="【大】">別</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">別異</rdg></app>也。彼時，男
<lb n="0421b08" ed="T"/>女之類意欲大小便時地自然開，事訖之後
<lb n="0421b09" ed="T"/>地<note n="0421025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝復【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便【大】，復【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421025"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復</rdg></app>還合。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421b0905" rend="inline">「爾時，閻浮地內自然生粳米，亦
<lb n="0421b10" ed="T"/>無皮裹，極為香美，食無患苦。所謂金、銀、珍
<lb n="0421b11" ed="T"/>寶、車𤦲、馬瑙、真珠、虎珀，各散在地，無人省錄。
<lb n="0421b12" ed="T"/>是時，人民手執此寶，自相謂言：『昔者之人由
<lb n="0421b13" ed="T"/>此寶故<note n="0421026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">更＝各【宮】</note><note n="0421026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">更【大】，各【宮】</note><app n="0421026"><lem wit="【大】">更</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">各</rdg></app>相傷害，繫閉在獄<note n="0421027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝更【宮】</note><note n="0421027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受【大】，更【宮】</note><app n="0421027"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">更</rdg></app>無數苦
<lb n="0421b14" ed="T"/>惱；如今此寶與瓦石同流，無人守護。』</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421b1415" rend="inline">「爾
<lb n="0421b15" ed="T"/>時，法王出現，名曰<note n="0421028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蠰佉＝儴佉【三】【宮】下同</note><note n="0421028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蠰佉【大】下同，儴佉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note><app n="0421028"><lem wit="【大】">蠰佉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">儴佉</rdg></app>。正法治化，七寶
<lb n="0421b16" ed="T"/>成就。所謂七寶者，<note n="0421029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（金）＋輪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">輪【大】，金輪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421029"><lem wit="【大】">輪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">金輪</rdg></app>寶、象寶、馬寶、珠寶、玉
<lb n="0421b17" ed="T"/>女寶、典兵寶、守藏<note n="0421030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421030"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>寶，是謂七寶。鎮此閻
<lb n="0421b18" ed="T"/>浮地內，不以刀杖自然靡伏。如今，阿難！四
<lb n="0421b19" ed="T"/>珍之藏：乾陀越國伊羅鉢寶藏，多諸珍<note n="0421031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">琦＝寶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">琦【大】，寶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421031"><lem wit="【大】">琦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">寶</rdg></app>
<lb n="0421b20" ed="T"/>異物不可稱計；第二彌<note n="0421032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">挮＝提【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">梯【大】，提【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421032"><lem wit="【大】">梯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">提</rdg></app>羅國<note n="0421033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">綢羅＝般綢【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">綢羅【大】，般綢【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421033"><lem wit="【大】">綢羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">般綢</rdg></app>大
<lb n="0421b21" ed="T"/>藏，亦多珍寶；第三須賴吒大國有大寶藏，
<lb n="0421b22" ed="T"/>亦多珍寶；第四<note n="0421b2201" resp="CBETA" type="add">婆【CB】【麗-CB】，波【大】</note><app n="0421b2201"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">婆<note type="cf1">K11n0197_p0209c10</note><note type="cf2">T02n0125_p0788a17</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">波</rdg></app>羅<note n="0421034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">㮈＋（國）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">㮈【大】，㮈國【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421034"><lem wit="【大】">㮈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">㮈國</rdg></app>蠰佉<note n="0421035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔有〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421035"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>大寶藏，
<lb n="0421b23" ed="T"/><note n="0421036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（亦）＋多【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">多【大】，亦多【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421036"><lem wit="【大】">多</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">亦多</rdg></app>諸珍寶不可稱計。此四大藏自然應現，
<lb n="0421b24" ed="T"/>諸守藏人各來白王：『唯願大王以此寶藏之
<lb n="0421b25" ed="T"/>物惠施貧窮。』爾時，蠰佉大王得此寶已，亦
<lb n="0421b26" ed="T"/>復不省錄之，<note n="0421037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意＝竟【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意【大】，竟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421037"><lem wit="【大】">意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">竟</rdg></app>無財<note n="0421038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寶＝物【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">寶【大】，物【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421038"><lem wit="【大】">寶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">物</rdg></app>之想。時閻浮地
<lb n="0421b27" ed="T"/>內，自然樹上生衣，極細柔軟，人取著之，如
<lb n="0421b28" ed="T"/>今優單越人自然樹上生衣，而無有異。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421b2816" rend="inline">「爾
<lb n="0421b29" ed="T"/>時，彼王有大臣名曰修梵摩，是王少小同好，
<pb n="0421c" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0453.0421c"/>
<lb n="0421c01" ed="T"/>王甚愛敬；又且顏貌端正，不長、不短，不肥、不
<lb n="0421c02" ed="T"/>瘦，不白、不黑，不老、不少。是時，修梵摩有妻
<lb n="0421c03" ed="T"/>名梵摩越，<note n="0421039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝玉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王【大】，玉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421039"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">玉</rdg></app>女中最極<note n="0421040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔為〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421040"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>殊妙，如天帝
<lb n="0421c04" ed="T"/>妃——口作優鉢<note n="0421041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蓮＝羅【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蓮【大】，羅【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421041"><lem wit="【大】">蓮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">羅</rdg></app>華香，身作栴檀香；諸婦人
<lb n="0421c05" ed="T"/>八十四態永無復有，亦無疾病亂想之念。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421c0517" rend="inline">「爾
<lb n="0421c06" ed="T"/>時，彌勒菩薩於兜率天，觀察父母不老不
<lb n="0421c07" ed="T"/>少，便降神下應從右脇生，如我今日右脇
<lb n="0421c08" ed="T"/>生無異，彌勒菩薩亦復如是。兜率諸天各
<lb n="0421c09" ed="T"/>各唱令：『彌勒菩薩已降神生。』</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421c0912" rend="inline">「是時，修梵摩
<lb n="0421c10" ed="T"/>即與子立字，名曰彌勒。彌勒菩薩有三十
<lb n="0421c11" ed="T"/>二相、八十種好莊嚴其身，身黃金色。爾時，人
<lb n="0421c12" ed="T"/>壽極長，無有諸患，皆壽八萬四千歲。女人
<lb n="0421c13" ed="T"/><note n="0421042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔年〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">年【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421042"><lem wit="【大】">年</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>五百歲然後出嫡。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421c1309" rend="inline">「爾時，彌勒在家未經
<lb n="0421c14" ed="T"/>幾時，便當出家學道。爾時，去翅頭城不
<lb n="0421c15" ed="T"/>遠有道樹名曰龍花，高一由旬，廣五百步。
<lb n="0421c16" ed="T"/>時彌勒菩薩坐彼樹下成無上道果。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421c1615" rend="inline">「當其
<lb n="0421c17" ed="T"/>夜半彌勒出家，即<note n="0421043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔於〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">於【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421043"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>其<note n="0421044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夜＋（分）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">夜【大】，夜分【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421044"><lem wit="【大】">夜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">夜分</rdg></app>成無上道。<note n="0421045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（應）＋時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時【大】，應時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421045"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">應時</rdg></app>
<lb n="0421c18" ed="T"/>三千大千剎土六<note n="0421046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">返＝反【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">返【大】，反【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421046"><lem wit="【大】">返</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">反</rdg></app>震動，地神各<note n="0421047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">各＋（而）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">各【大】，各而【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421047"><lem wit="【大】">各</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">各而</rdg></app>相告
<lb n="0421c19" ed="T"/>曰：『今<note n="0421048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔時〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421048"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>彌勒已成<note n="0421049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＋（道其聲）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，佛道其聲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421049"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">佛道其聲</rdg></app>。』轉至聞四天王宮：『彌
<lb n="0421c20" ed="T"/>勒已成佛道。』轉<note n="0421050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔轉〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">轉【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421050"><lem wit="【大】">轉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>聞<note n="0421051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">徹＋（於）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">徹【大】，徹於【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421051"><lem wit="【大】">徹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">徹於</rdg></app>三十三天、<note n="0421052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">豔＝燄摩【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">豔【大】，燄摩【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421052"><lem wit="【大】">豔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">燄摩</rdg></app>天、
<lb n="0421c21" ed="T"/>兜<note n="0421053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">率＋（陀）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">率【大】，率陀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421053"><lem wit="【大】">率</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">率陀</rdg></app>天、化<note n="0421054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自在＝樂【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自在【大】，樂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421054"><lem wit="【大】">自在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">樂</rdg></app>天、他<note n="0421055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">化＋（化）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">化【大】，化化【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421055"><lem wit="【大】">化</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">化化</rdg></app>自在天，<note n="0421056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聲聞展轉至＝乃至【三】【宮】</note><note n="0421056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聲聞展轉至【大】，乃至【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0421056"><lem wit="【大】">聲聞展
<lb n="0421c22" ed="T"/>轉至</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">乃至</rdg></app>梵天：『彌勒已成佛道。』</p><p xml:id="pT14p0421c2211" rend="inline">「爾時，魔王名大
<lb n="0421c23" ed="T"/>將，以法治化。聞如來名音響之聲，歡喜踊躍
<lb n="0421c24" ed="T"/>不能自勝，七日七夜不眠不寐。是時，魔王
<lb n="0421c25" ed="T"/>將欲界無數<note n="0421057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天人＝人天【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0421057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天人【大】＊，人天【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0421057"><lem wit="【大】">天人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">人天</rdg></app>至彌勒佛所恭敬禮拜。</p>
<pb n="0422a" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0453.0422a"/>
<lb n="0422a01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0422a0101">「彌勒聖尊與諸<app type="star" corresp="#0421057"><lem wit="【大】">天人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">人天</rdg></app>漸漸說法微妙之論，
<lb n="0422a02" ed="T"/>所謂論者，施論、戒論、生天之論，欲不淨想、出
<lb n="0422a03" ed="T"/>要為妙。爾時，彌勒見諸人民已發心歡喜，
<lb n="0422a04" ed="T"/>諸佛世尊常所說法，苦、<note n="0422001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">習＝集【三】【宮】下同</note><note n="0422001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">習【大】下同，集【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note><app n="0422001"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">集</rdg></app>、盡、道，<note n="0422002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔盡〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盡【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422002"><lem wit="【大】">盡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>與諸天
<lb n="0422a05" ed="T"/>人廣分別其義。爾時，座上八萬四千天子，諸
<lb n="0422a06" ed="T"/>塵垢盡，得法眼淨。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422a0608" rend="inline">「爾時，大將魔王告彼界人
<lb n="0422a07" ed="T"/>民之類曰：『汝等速出家。所以然者？彌勒今
<lb n="0422a08" ed="T"/>日已度彼岸，亦當度汝等使至彼岸。』</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422a0815" rend="inline">「爾時，
<lb n="0422a09" ed="T"/>翅頭城中<note n="0422003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有＋（一）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有【大】，有一【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422003"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">有一</rdg></app>長者名曰善財，聞魔王教令，
<lb n="0422a10" ed="T"/>又聞佛音響，將八萬四千眾至彌勒佛所，
<lb n="0422a11" ed="T"/>頭面禮足，在一面坐。</p>
<lb n="0422a12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0422a1201">「爾時，彌勒漸<note n="0422004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">與＝為【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0422004" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->與【大】＊，為【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0422004"><lem wit="【大】">與</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">為</rdg></app>說法微妙之論，所謂論者，
<lb n="0422a13" ed="T"/>施論、戒論、生天之論，欲不淨想、出要為妙。爾
<lb n="0422a14" ed="T"/>時，彌勒見諸人民心開意解，如諸佛世尊常
<lb n="0422a15" ed="T"/>所說法，苦、習、盡、道，與諸<note n="0422005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人民＝天人【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人民【大】，天人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422005"><lem wit="【大】">人民</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">天人</rdg></app>廣分別
<lb n="0422a16" ed="T"/><note n="0422006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（其）＋義【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">義【大】，其義【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422006"><lem wit="【大】">義</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">其義</rdg></app>。爾時，座上八萬四千人諸塵垢盡，得法
<lb n="0422a17" ed="T"/>眼淨。是時，善財與八萬四千人等即前白
<lb n="0422a18" ed="T"/>佛，求索出家，善修梵行，盡成<note n="0422007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">阿羅漢道＝羅漢道果【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">阿羅漢道【大】，羅漢道果【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422007"><lem wit="【大】">阿羅漢道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">羅漢道果</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0422a19" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0422a1901">「爾時，彌勒初會，八萬四千<note n="0422008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人得〕－【宮】</note><note n="0422008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人得【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0422008"><lem wit="【大】">人得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>阿羅漢。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422a1916" rend="inline">「是時，
<lb n="0422a20" ed="T"/>蠰佉王聞彌勒已成佛道，便往至佛所
<lb n="0422a21" ed="T"/>欲得聞法。時彌勒佛與王說法，初善、中善、
<lb n="0422a22" ed="T"/><note n="0422009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">竟＝後【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">竟【大】，後【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422009"><lem wit="【大】">竟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">後</rdg></app>善，義理深邃。爾時，大王復於異時立太
<lb n="0422a23" ed="T"/>子為王，賜剃頭師珍寶，復以雜寶與諸梵
<lb n="0422a24" ed="T"/>志，將八萬四千眾往至佛所求作沙門，盡
<lb n="0422a25" ed="T"/>成道果得阿羅漢。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422a2508" rend="inline">「是時，修梵摩大長者聞
<lb n="0422a26" ed="T"/>彌勒已成佛道，將八萬四千梵志之眾往
<lb n="0422a27" ed="T"/>至佛所求作沙門，得<note n="0422010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔阿〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0422010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">阿【大】＊，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0422010"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>羅<note n="0422011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">漢＋（果）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">漢【大】，漢果【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422011"><lem wit="【大】">漢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">漢果</rdg></app>——唯修梵摩一
<lb n="0422a28" ed="T"/>人斷三結使必盡苦際。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422a2810" rend="inline">「是時，佛母梵摩越
<lb n="0422a29" ed="T"/>復將八萬四千婇女之眾往至佛所求作
<pb n="0422b" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0453.0422b"/>
<lb n="0422b01" ed="T"/>沙門。爾時，諸女<note n="0422012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422012"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>盡得<app type="star" corresp="#0422010"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>羅漢——唯有梵摩
<lb n="0422b02" ed="T"/>越一人斷三結使成須陀洹。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422b0212" rend="inline">「爾時，諸剎利
<lb n="0422b03" ed="T"/>婦聞彌勒如來出現世間成等正覺，數千
<lb n="0422b04" ed="T"/>萬眾往至佛所，頭面禮足，在一面坐，各各
<lb n="0422b05" ed="T"/>生心求作沙門，出家學道，或有越次取
<lb n="0422b06" ed="T"/>證、或有不取證者。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422b0608" rend="inline">「爾時，阿難！其不越次取
<lb n="0422b07" ed="T"/>證者盡是奉法之人，<note n="0422013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">患厭＝厭患【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">患厭【大】，厭患【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422013"><lem wit="【大】">患厭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">厭患</rdg></app>一切世間，<note n="0422014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔修〕－【三】</note><note n="0422014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">修【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0422014"><lem wit="【大】">修</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0422b08" ed="T"/>不可樂想。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422b0805" rend="inline">「爾時，彌勒當說三乘<note n="0422015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422015"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>教，如我
<lb n="0422b09" ed="T"/>今<note n="0422016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">日＝也【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">日【大】，也【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422016"><lem wit="【大】">日</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">也</rdg></app>。弟子之中大迦葉者行十二頭陀、過
<lb n="0422b10" ed="T"/>去諸佛所善修梵行，此人當佐彌<note n="0422017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勒＋（佛）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">勒【大】，勒佛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422017"><lem wit="【大】">勒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">勒佛</rdg></app>勸化
<lb n="0422b11" ed="T"/>人民。」</p>
<lb n="0422b12" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0422b1201">爾時，迦葉去如來不遠結加趺坐，正身正意
<lb n="0422b13" ed="T"/>繫念在前。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422b1305" rend="inline">爾時，世尊告迦葉曰：「吾今年已
<lb n="0422b14" ed="T"/>衰耗向八十餘。然今如來有四大聲聞堪任
<lb n="0422b15" ed="T"/>遊化，智慧無盡，眾德具足。云何為四？所謂大
<lb n="0422b16" ed="T"/>迦葉比丘、<note n="0422018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（君）＋屠【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">屠【大】，君屠【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422018"><lem wit="【大】">屠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">君屠</rdg></app>鉢歎比丘、賓頭盧比丘、羅
<lb n="0422b17" ed="T"/>云比丘。汝等四大聲聞要不般涅槃，須吾
<lb n="0422b18" ed="T"/>法沒盡，然後乃當般涅槃。大迦葉亦不應
<lb n="0422b19" ed="T"/>般涅槃，<note n="0422019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">要須＝須待【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">要須【大】，須待【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422019"><lem wit="【大】">要須</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">須待</rdg></app>彌勒出現世間。所以然者，
<lb n="0422b20" ed="T"/>彌勒所化弟子盡是釋迦<note n="0422020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">文＋（佛）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">文【大】，文佛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422020"><lem wit="【大】">文</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">文佛</rdg></app>弟子，由我遺
<lb n="0422b21" ed="T"/>化得盡有漏。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422b2106" rend="inline">「摩竭國界毘提村中，大迦葉
<lb n="0422b22" ed="T"/>於彼山中住。又彌勒如來將無數千人<note n="0422021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔眾〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眾【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422021"><lem wit="【大】">眾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，
<lb n="0422b23" ed="T"/>前後圍遶往至此山中，遂蒙佛恩，諸鬼神
<lb n="0422b24" ed="T"/>當與開門，使得見迦葉禪窟。是時，彌勒
<lb n="0422b25" ed="T"/>申右手指示迦葉，告諸人民：『過去久遠釋
<lb n="0422b26" ed="T"/>迦文佛弟子名曰迦葉，今日現在，頭陀苦行
<lb n="0422b27" ed="T"/>最為第一。』是時，諸人見是事已歎未曾有，
<lb n="0422b28" ed="T"/>無數百千眾生諸塵垢盡，得法眼淨。或<note n="0422022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422022"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0422b29" ed="T"/>有眾生見迦葉身已——此名為最初之會——九
<pb n="0422c" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0453.0422c"/>
<lb n="0422c01" ed="T"/>十六億人皆得阿羅漢，斯等之人皆是我弟
<lb n="0422c02" ed="T"/>子。所以然者？悉由受<note n="0422023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我＋（教）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我【大】，我教【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422023"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">我教</rdg></app>訓之所致也，亦
<lb n="0422c03" ed="T"/>由四事因緣：惠施、仁愛、利人、等利。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422c0314" rend="inline">「<note n="0422024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">爾時阿難＝阿難爾時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">爾時阿難【大】，阿難爾時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422024"><lem wit="【大】">爾時，阿難</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">阿難爾時</rdg></app>！
<lb n="0422c04" ed="T"/>彌勒如來當取迦葉僧伽梨著之。是時，迦
<lb n="0422c05" ed="T"/>葉身體奄然星散。是時，彌勒復取種種華香
<lb n="0422c06" ed="T"/>供養迦葉。所以然者？諸佛世尊有敬心於
<lb n="0422c07" ed="T"/>正法故。彌勒亦由我所受正法化，得成無
<lb n="0422c08" ed="T"/>上正真之道。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422c0806" rend="inline">「阿難當知，彌勒佛第二會時，有
<lb n="0422c09" ed="T"/>九十四億人，皆<note n="0422025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是【大】，得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422025"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">得</rdg></app>阿羅漢，亦復是我遺教弟
<lb n="0422c10" ed="T"/>子，行四事供養之所致也。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422c1011" rend="inline">「又彌勒第<anchor xml:id="fxT14p0422c01"/>三之
<lb n="0422c11" ed="T"/>會，九十二億人<note n="0422026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皆是＝得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆是【大】，得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422026"><lem wit="【大】">皆是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">得</rdg></app>阿羅漢，亦復是我遺
<lb n="0422c12" ed="T"/>教弟子。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422c1204" rend="inline">「爾時，比丘姓號皆<note n="0422027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">名＝曰【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">名【大】，曰【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422027"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">曰</rdg></app>慈氏弟子，如
<lb n="0422c13" ed="T"/>我今日諸聲聞皆稱釋迦弟子。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0422c1313" rend="inline">「爾時，彌勒與
<lb n="0422c14" ed="T"/>諸弟子說法：『汝等比丘！當思惟無常之想、
<lb n="0422c15" ed="T"/>樂有苦想、計我無我想、實有空想、色變之想、
<lb n="0422c16" ed="T"/>青瘀之想、膖脹之想、食不消想、<note n="0422028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">膿＝想【宮】</note><note n="0422028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">膿【大】，想【宮】</note><app n="0422028"><lem wit="【大】">膿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">想</rdg></app>血想、
<lb n="0422c17" ed="T"/>一切世間不可樂想。所以然者？比丘當
<lb n="0422c18" ed="T"/>知，此十想者皆是過去釋迦文佛與汝
<lb n="0422c19" ed="T"/>等說，令得盡有漏、心得解脫。若此眾中
<lb n="0422c20" ed="T"/>釋迦文佛弟子，過去<note n="0422029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（之）＋時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時【大】，之時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422029"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">之時</rdg></app>修於梵行，來至
<lb n="0422c21" ed="T"/>我所；或<note n="0422030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422030"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>於釋迦文<note n="0422031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佛＋（所奉持其法來至我所或復於釋迦文佛）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，佛所奉持其法來至我所或復於釋迦文佛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422031"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">佛所奉持其法來至我所或復於釋迦文佛</rdg></app>所供養三寶，來
<lb n="0422c22" ed="T"/>至我所；或於釋迦文佛所彈指之頃修於善
<lb n="0422c23" ed="T"/>本，來至此間；或於釋迦文佛所行四等心，
<lb n="0422c24" ed="T"/>來至此者；或於釋迦文佛所受持五戒、三
<lb n="0422c25" ed="T"/>自歸法，來至我所；或於釋迦文佛所起<note n="0422032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">神＝立【三】【宮】</note><note n="0422032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">神【大】，立【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0422032"><lem wit="【大】">神</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">立</rdg></app>
<lb n="0422c26" ed="T"/>寺廟，來至我所；或於釋迦文佛所補治故
<lb n="0422c27" ed="T"/>寺，來至我所；或於釋迦文佛所受八關齋
<lb n="0422c28" ed="T"/>法，來至我所；或於釋迦文佛所香華供養，
<lb n="0422c29" ed="T"/>來至此者；或復於彼聞法悲泣墮淚，
<pb n="0423a" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0453.0423a"/>
<lb n="0423a01" ed="T"/>來至我所；或復於釋迦文佛所專<note n="0423001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意＝心【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意【大】，心【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423001"><lem wit="【大】">意</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">心</rdg></app>聽
<lb n="0423a02" ed="T"/><note n="0423002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔受〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423002"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>法，來至我所；或復盡形壽<note n="0423003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善修梵行＝善持禁戒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善修梵行【大】，善持禁戒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423003"><lem wit="【大】">善修梵行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">善持禁戒</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0423a03" ed="T"/>來至我所；或<note n="0423004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＋（盡形壽善持梵行來至我所或復）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復【大】，復盡形壽善持梵行來至我所或復【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423004"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">復盡形壽善持梵行來至我所或復</rdg></app>有<note n="0423005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">書寫讀誦＝書讀諷誦【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">書寫讀誦【大】，書讀諷誦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423005"><lem wit="【大】">書寫讀誦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">書讀諷誦</rdg></app>，來至我所；
<lb n="0423a04" ed="T"/>或復承事供養，來至我所者。』</p><p xml:id="pT14p0423a0412" rend="inline">「<note n="0423006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝爾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是【大】，爾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423006"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">爾</rdg></app>時，彌勒便
<lb n="0423a05" ed="T"/>說<note n="0423007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此偈＝偈言【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此偈【大】，偈言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423007"><lem wit="【大】">此偈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">偈言</rdg></app>：</p>
<lb n="0423a06" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT14p0423a0601" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-2em"><l>「『增益戒聞德，</l><l>禪及思惟業，</l>
<lb n="0423a07" ed="T"/><l>善修於梵行，</l><l>而來至我所。</l>
<lb n="0423a08" ed="T"/><l>勸<note n="0423008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">施＝於【元】</note><note n="0423008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">施【大】，於【元】</note><app n="0423008"><lem wit="【大】">施</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">於</rdg></app>發歡心，</l><l>修行心原本，</l>
<lb n="0423a09" ed="T"/><l>意無若干想，</l><l>皆來至我所。</l>
<lb n="0423a10" ed="T"/><l><note n="0423009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＝欲【三】</note><note n="0423009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">或【大】，欲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0423009"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">欲</rdg></app>發平等心，</l><l>承事於諸佛，</l>
<lb n="0423a11" ed="T"/><l>飯<note n="0423010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飴＝食【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飴【大】，食【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423010"><lem wit="【大】">飴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">食</rdg></app>於聖眾，</l><l>皆來至我所。</l>
<lb n="0423a12" ed="T"/><l><note n="0423011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＝所【三】</note><note n="0423011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">或【大】，所【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0423011"><lem wit="【大】">或</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">所</rdg></app>誦戒契經，</l><l><note n="0423012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善＝若【宮】</note><note n="0423012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">善【大】，若【宮】</note><app n="0423012"><lem wit="【大】">善</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">若</rdg></app>習與人說，</l>
<lb n="0423a13" ed="T"/><l><note n="0423013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">熾然＝然熾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">熾然【大】，然熾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423013"><lem wit="【大】">熾然</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">然熾</rdg></app>於法本，</l><l>今來至我所。</l>
<lb n="0423a14" ed="T"/><l>釋種善能化，</l><l>供養諸舍利，</l>
<lb n="0423a15" ed="T"/><l>承事法供養，</l><l>今來至我所。</l>
<lb n="0423a16" ed="T"/><l>若有書寫經，</l><l><note n="0423014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">班＝頒【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">班【大】，頒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423014"><lem wit="【大】">班</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">頒</rdg></app>宣於素上，</l>
<lb n="0423a17" ed="T"/><l>其有供養<note n="0423015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＝者【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423015"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">者</rdg></app>，</l><l>皆來至<note n="0423016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我＝佛【元】</note><note n="0423016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我【大】，佛【元】</note><app n="0423016"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】">佛</rdg></app>所。</l>
<lb n="0423a18" ed="T"/><l>繒綵及諸物，</l><l>供養於<note n="0423017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">神寺＝塔等【三】，塔寺【宮】</note><note n="0423017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">神寺【大】，塔等【宋】【元】【明】，塔寺【宮】</note><app n="0423017"><lem wit="【大】">神寺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">塔等</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">塔寺</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0423a19" ed="T"/><l>自稱南無佛，</l><l>皆來至我所。</l>
<lb n="0423a20" ed="T"/><l>供養於現在、</l><l>諸佛過去者，</l>
<lb n="0423a21" ed="T"/><l>禪定正平等，</l><l>亦無有增減。</l>
<lb n="0423a22" ed="T"/><l>是故於佛法，</l><l>承事於聖眾，</l>
<lb n="0423a23" ed="T"/><l>專心事三寶，</l><l>必至無為處。』</l></lg>
<lb n="0423a24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0423a2401">「阿難當知，彌勒如來在彼眾中當說此偈。
<lb n="0423a25" ed="T"/>爾時，彼眾中諸天人民思惟此十想，十一姟
<lb n="0423a26" ed="T"/>人諸塵垢盡，得法眼淨。彌勒如來千歲之中，
<lb n="0423a27" ed="T"/>眾僧無有瑕穢。爾時，恒以一偈<note n="0423018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】</note><note n="0423018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，已【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0423018"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">已</rdg></app>為禁
<lb n="0423a28" ed="T"/>戒：</p>
<lb n="0423a29" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT14p0423a2901" rend="margin-left:2em;text-indent:-2em"><l>「『口、意不行惡，</l><l>身亦無所犯，</l>
<pb n="0423b" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0453.0423b"/>
<lb n="0423b01" ed="T"/><l>當除此三行，</l><l>速脫生死關。』</l></lg>
<lb n="0423b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT14p0423b0201">「過千歲後，當有犯戒之人，遂復立戒。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0423b0215" rend="inline">「彌勒
<lb n="0423b03" ed="T"/>如來當壽八萬四千歲。般涅槃後，遺法當
<lb n="0423b04" ed="T"/><note n="0423019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝存【三】</note><note n="0423019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在【大】，存【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0423019"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">存</rdg></app>八萬四千歲。所以然者，爾時眾生皆是
<lb n="0423b05" ed="T"/>利根。</p><p xml:id="pT14p0423b0503" rend="inline">「其有善男子、善女人欲得見彌勒佛
<lb n="0423b06" ed="T"/>及三會聲聞眾及翅頭城及見蠰佉王并四
<lb n="0423b07" ed="T"/>大藏珍寶者、欲食自然粳米者、并著自然
<lb n="0423b08" ed="T"/>衣裳、身壞命終生天上者，彼善男子、善女
<lb n="0423b09" ed="T"/>人當勤加精進，無<note n="0423020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝得【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生【大】，得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423020"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">得</rdg></app>懈怠；亦當供養承
<lb n="0423b10" ed="T"/>事諸法師，名花㨶香種種供養，無令有失。
<lb n="0423b11" ed="T"/>如是，阿難！當作是學。」</p><p xml:id="pT14p0423b1109" rend="inline">爾時，阿難及諸大會，
<lb n="0423b12" ed="T"/>聞佛所說，歡喜奉行。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="0423b13" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="close"><cb:jhead><note n="0423021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【元】，佛說＝佛說觀【明】</note><note n="0423021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛說【大】，〔－〕【元】，佛說觀【明】</note><app n="0423021"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">佛說觀</rdg></app>彌勒下生經</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0423b14" ed="T"/><cb:div type="w"><p xml:id="pT14p0423b1401"><note n="0423022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔按開元…賢哲〕<g ref="#CB00849"/>文－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0423022" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->〔按開元…賢哲〕<g ref="#CB00849"/>文二百六十二字－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0423022" cb:word-count="262"><lem wit="【大】">按《開元錄》有譯無本中有法護譯《彌勒
<lb n="0423b15" ed="T"/>成佛經》，一名「彌勒當來下生經」者。乍觀此
<lb n="0423b16" ed="T"/>經即彼失本而還得之，其實非也。何則？羅
<lb n="0423b17" ed="T"/>什譯《彌勒成佛經》目下注云：「與《下生經》異
<lb n="0423b18" ed="T"/>本，與法護譯《彌勒成佛經》同本。」兩譯一闕，
<lb n="0423b19" ed="T"/>則彼失本經，非此《下生經》六譯三失之一
<lb n="0423b20" ed="T"/>者明矣。又按孤山智圓重校金剛般若後
<lb n="0423b21" ed="T"/>序云：「古德分經皆用紙數者，一紙有二
<lb n="0423b22" ed="T"/>十五行，一行十七字。今撿失本彌勒經目
<lb n="0423b23" ed="T"/>下注云：『一十七紙』，則計有七千二百二十
<lb n="0423b24" ed="T"/>二字，此經只有三千一百七十六字，則尚
<lb n="0423b25" ed="T"/>未其半，豈是彼經歟？」則丹藏無此經為
<lb n="0423b26" ed="T"/>得。然此經文頗似漢晉經注，又有漢云
<lb n="0423b27" ed="T"/>之言，還恐此是三失本中第一本。錄云今
<lb n="0423b28" ed="T"/>附西晉者耳，宋藏還得而編入之為得
<lb n="0423b29" ed="T"/>之矣。而二錄並無《下生經》是法護譯者，今
<pb n="0423c" ed="T" xml:id="T14.0453.0423c"/>
<lb n="0423c01" ed="T"/>云法護譯者何耶？伏俟賢哲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>